title: Avira Premium Security Suite Keys(07/19/2011)
description:
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
             Avira Premium Security Suite Working Keys 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------


All Keys are Tested and Working as of 07/19/2011.



**************  How to Apply These Keys   **************


1. Open Avira Security Suite.


2. Click on "Help - License management".

3.This opens the license wizard. click on hbedv.key.


 <a href="
http://img825.imageshack.us/img825/3456/31652379.png" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://img825.imageshack.us/img825/3456/31652379.png</a>



4. Navigate to the folder with your saved license file and Select the file by double-clicking on it.

5. Let it Update The License.

6. Done


******** Do Not Double click the key files and insert them*********
